OL,3,CNI pupils had 'astonishing' questions
OL,4,Cfor Prof Brian Cox
OL,6,FStudents in Northern Ireland put
OL,7,F"astonishing" questions to Professor
OL,8,FBrian Cox as he hosted an event aimed
OL,9,Fat inspiring the scientists, engineers
OL,10,Fand inventors of the future.
OL,12,FThe broadcaster and professor of
OL,13,Fparticle physics says the foundations
OL,14,Falready exist in the region to
OL,15,Fencourage many more young people
OL,16,Ftowards careers in science.
