OL,3,CNI pupils had 'astonishing' questions
OL,4,Cfor Prof Brian Cox
OL,6,FHe attended the Science Summer School
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland alongside educators
OL,8,Fand influencers from the world of
OL,9,Fscience, technology, engineering, the
OL,10,Farts and maths.
OL,12,F"They're all so curious," Professor
OL,13,FCox told UTV. "The questions I got
OL,14,Fwere quite astonishing, ranging from
OL,15,Fthe profound to the absurd actually!
OL,17,F"But it's also about showing these
OL,18,Fyoung people there are pathways into -
OL,19,Fit could be academic science,
OL,20,Fastronomy.
