OL,3,CNI pupils had 'astonishing' questions
OL,4,Cfor Prof Brian Cox
OL,6,F"Or it could be into the industry,
OL,7,Fwhich is growing rapidly in this area,
OL,8,Fmaking connections and really trying
OL,9,Fto show them routes should they want
OL,10,Fto wander down those roads."
OL,12,FFour hundred young people from local
OL,13,Fschools took part in the event on
OL,14,FTuesday, which included seminars,
OL,15,Fdiscussions and hands-on experiments.
