OL,4,Cfor Prof Brian Cox
OL,6,FProfessor Cox, who was formerly a
OL,7,Fkeyboard player with 90s pop group
OL,8,FD:Ream, said Northern Ireland's
OL,9,Fscientific and engineering heritage is
OL,10,Fbeing reawakened, with companies
OL,11,Fembracing new high-tech industries.
OL,13,F"If you want to work in a very high-
OL,14,Ftech engineering company there are a
OL,15,Flot of them on the doorstep here," he
OL,16,Fcontinued.
OL,18,F"Or if you want to be an astronomer,
OL,19,FArmagh is one of the world centres for
OL,20,Fastronomy.
