OL,3,CNI pupils had 'astonishing' questions
OL,4,Cfor Prof Brian Cox
OL,6,F"There is a space sciences industry
OL,7,Fhere. You can build satellites, you
OL,8,Fcan build aircraft, all those things
OL,9,Fare here, but I think sometimes people
OL,10,Fjust think it is not for them.
OL,12,F"When you talk to the industries here,
OL,13,Fthey are short of people, there are
OL,14,Fmore jobs than there are people who
OL,15,Fare qualified or trained to do those
OL,16,Fjobs.
OL,18,F"We need, whether it is basic science
OL,19,For research or industry, to draw
OL,20,Ftalent from as wide a pool as possible.
