OL,3,CNI pupils had 'astonishing' questions
OL,4,Cfor Prof Brian Cox
OL,6,F"This area is making that
OL,7,Ftransformation into the new industries
OL,8,Fof the 21st century really
OL,9,Fsuccessfully.
OL,11,F"You see a great deal of high tech
OL,12,Fengineering companies in this area
OL,13,Fbecause the infrastructure is here and
OL,14,Fthe heritage is here.
OL,16,F"Those are things that are very
OL,17,Fdifficult to get. What you see in this
OL,18,Fregion is that the foundations are
OL,19,Fsolid, they stretch back a long time.
